# RealTime Output Commands

<noinclude>These commands are used to monitor the state of the model at any time during the simulation. These include:</noinclude>

Model Quantities
  • eleNodes Command
  • getEleTags Command
  • getNodeTags
  • nodeBounds
  • print Command
Response Quantities
  • eleResponse Command
  • nodeDisp Command
  • nodeVel Command
  • nodeAccel Command
  • getTime Command
